description.en: Here she is! The much beloved and rare Monstera Thai Constellation! Isnâ€™t she absolutely gorgeous?! This is a rare Monstera species that you will not find in nature. This is because she was especially created to have stable variegation. She will never stop giving you her amazing variegated leaves.
